      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASSENITE (6) finished in fifth when tackling a dirt track for the first time last start over this track and trip. Looked at home on this surface and will be hard to beat this time. STAR POWER (2) finished second when resuming two runs back at Rockingham then progressed nicely last time out to score by 0.7 lengths as public elect over 1200m at this track. Best figures measure up. Sure to run well. FAMEUX (3) made progress last start to finish second over 1200m at this track after being in the firing line on the corner. Has his share of talent. Hard to beat in this suitable race. LEADING TADDY (4) was returning from a break last time out and proved too classy, scoring by half a length over 1300m at this track. Fitter for that last hitout and cannot be ruled out. ADRETT (5) has to be included on her latest effort.",
